{"word":"Moses","slug":"moses","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Moses</b> <a href=\"#/H4872\">H4872</a><br/><a href=\"#/H4873\">H4873</a> <br/> History of:<br/> - A Levite and son of Amram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=4'>Exo 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=20'>Exo 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=20'>Act 7:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=23'>Heb 11:23</a> <br/> - Hidden in an ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=3'>Exo 2:3</a> <br/> - Discovered and adopted by the daughter of Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=10'>Exo 2:10</a> <br/> - Learned in all the wisdom of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=22'>Act 7:22</a> <br/> - His loyalty to his race<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=26'>Heb 11:26</a> <br/> - Takes the life of an Egyptian; flees from Egypt; finds refuge among the Midianites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=22'>Exo 2:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=29'>Act 7:29</a> <br/> - Joins himself to Jethro, priest of Midian; marries his daughter Zipporah; has one son, Gershom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=22'>Exo 2:22</a> <br/> - Is herdman for Jethro in the desert of Horeb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=1'>Exo 3:1</a> <br/> - Has the vision of the burning bush<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=6'>Exo 3:6</a> <br/> - God reveals to him His purpose to deliver the Israelites and bring them into the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=10'>Exo 3:10</a> <br/> - Commissioned as leader of the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=22'>Exo 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=13'>Exo 6:13</a> <br/> - His rod miraculously turned into a serpent, and his hand made leprous, and each restored<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=9'>Exo 4:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=28'>Exo 4:28</a> <br/> - With his wife and sons leaves Jethro to perform his mission<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=20'>Exo 4:20</a> <br/> - His controversy with his wife on account of circumcision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=26'>Exo 4:26</a> <br/> - Meets Aaron in the wilderness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=28'>Exo 4:28</a> <br/> - With Aaron assembles the leaders of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=31'>Exo 4:31</a> <br/> - With Aaron goes before Pharaoh, in the name of Jehovah demands the liberties of his people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=1'>Exo 5:1</a> <br/> - Rejected by Pharaoh; hardships of the Israelites increased<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5'>Exo 5</a> <br/> - People murmur against Moses and Aaron<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=21'>Exo 5:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=24'>Exo 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=3'>Exo 16:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=3'>Exo 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=4'>Num 14:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=41'>Num 16:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=5'>Num 20:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=6'>Num 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=12'>Deu 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=28'>Deu 1:28</a><br/><a href='S:Israel'>Israel</a><br/> - Receives comfort and assurance from the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=8'>Exo 6:8</a> <br/> - Unbelief of the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=9'>Exo 6:9</a> <br/> - Renews his appeal to Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=11'>Exo 6:11</a> <br/> - Under divine direction brings plagues upon the land of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7'>Exo 7</a> <br/> - Secures the deliverance of the people and leads them out of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13'>Exo 13</a> <br/> - Crosses the Red Sea; Pharaoh and his army are destroyed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14'>Exo 14</a> <br/> - Composes a song for the children of Israel on their deliverance from Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15'>Exo 15</a> <br/> - Joined by his family in the wilderness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=18&verse=12'>Exo 18:12</a> <br/> - Institutes a system of government<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=18&verse=26'>Exo 18:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=30'>Num 11:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=18'>Deu 1:18</a> <br/> - Receives the law and ordains diverse statutes<br/> <a href='S:Law, Of Moses'>Law, Of Moses</a> <br/> - Face of, transfigured<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=35'>Exo 34:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=3&verse=13'>2Co 3:13</a> <br/> - Sets up the tabernacle<br/> <a href='S:Tabernacle'>Tabernacle</a> <br/> - Reproves Aaron:<br/> b for making the golden calf<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=23'>Exo 32:23</a><br/> b for irregularity in the offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=20'>Lev 10:20</a><br/> - Jealousy of Aaron and Miriam toward<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12'>Num 12</a> <br/> - Rebellion of Korah, Dathan, and Abiram against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16'>Num 16</a> <br/> - Appoints Joshua as his successor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=23'>Num 27:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=8'>Deu 31:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=14'>Deu 31:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=23'>Deu 31:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=9'>Deu 34:9</a> <br/> - Not permitted to enter Canaan, but views the land from Mount Pisgah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=14'>Num 27:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=37'>Deu 1:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=29'>Deu 3:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=52'>Deu 32:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=8'>Deu 34:8</a> <br/> - Death and burial of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=2'>Num 31:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=50'>Deu 32:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=6'>Deu 34:6</a> <br/> - Body of, disputed over<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - One hundred and twenty years old at death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=2'>Deu 31:2</a> <br/> - Mourning for, thirty days in the plains of Moab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=8'>Deu 34:8</a> <br/> - His virility<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=2'>Deu 31:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=7'>Deu 34:7</a> <br/> - Present with Jesus on the mount of transfiguration<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=4'>Mat 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=4'>Mar 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=30'>Luk 9:30</a> <br/> - Type of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=18'>Deu 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=22'>Act 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=37'>Act 7:37</a> <br/> Benedictions of:<br/> - Upon the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9&verse=23'>Lev 9:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=36'>Num 10:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=11'>Deu 1:11</a> <br/> - Last benediction upon the twelve tribes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33'>Deu 33</a> <br/> Character of:<br/> - Murmurings of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=23'>Exo 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=15'>Num 11:15</a> <br/> - Impatience of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=23'>Exo 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=12'>Exo 6:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=19'>Exo 32:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=15'>Num 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=15'>Num 16:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=10'>Num 20:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=14'>Num 31:14</a> <br/> - Respected and feared<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=8'>Exo 33:8</a> <br/> - Faith of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=29'>Num 10:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=3'>Deu 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=28'>Heb 11:28</a> <br/> - Called the man of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=1'>Deu 33:1</a> <br/> - God spake to, as a man to his friend<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=11'>Exo 33:11</a> <br/> - Magnified of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=9'>Exo 19:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=20'>Num 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=29'>Deu 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=30'>Exo 32:30</a> <br/> - Magnanimity of, toward Eldad and Medad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=29'>Num 11:29</a> <br/> - Meekness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=14'>Exo 14:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=25'>Exo 15:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=3'>Exo 16:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=8'>Exo 16:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=3'>Num 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=11'>Num 16:11</a> <br/> - Obedience of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=6'>Exo 7:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=16'>Exo 40:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=19'>Exo 40:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=21'>Exo 40:21</a> <br/> - Unaspiring<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=20'>Num 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=29'>Deu 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=30'>Exo 32:30</a> <br/> Intercessory prayers of<br/> <a href='S:Intercession, Of Man with Man, Instances of'>Intercession, Of Man with Man, Instances of</a>; <a href='S:Intercession, Solicited, Instances of'>Intercession, Solicited, Instances of</a>; <a href='S:Intercession, Answered, Instances of'>Intercession, Answered, Instances of</a><br/> Miracles of<br/> <a href='S:Miracles, Catalogue of'>Miracles, Catalogue of</a><br/> Prophecies of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=10'>Exo 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=5'>Exo 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=12'>Exo 4:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=13'>Exo 6:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=2'>Exo 7:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=16'>Exo 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=9'>Exo 19:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=11'>Exo 33:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=17'>Num 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=8'>Num 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=36&verse=13'>Num 36:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=3'>Deu 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=31'>Deu 5:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=15'>Deu 18:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=18'>Deu 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=10'>Deu 34:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=12'>Deu 34:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=12&verse=13'>Hos 12:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=10'>Mar 7:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=38'>Act 7:38</a>"}]}